<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Takes as long as it takes. Share and enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Play music in the kitchen. <a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/spotify/playlist/37i9dQZF1DWUofLlXqRWZz?si=USn4-F9USKyABFz6jLhhtg">I recommend this playlist.</a></li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>Place the lard in a sauce pan, and add the finely chopped onions to fry.</li>
  <li>add the chopped mushrooms and sliced leek and wait until it goes soft.</li>
  <li>now add the chicken and season with salt and pepper.</li>
  <li>add the rice, and pore the wine on it. Stir until wine is absorbed.</li>
  <li>add the herb mix and gradually add the stock until the rice goes sticky.</li>
  <li>At the end grate the garlic on the risotto and add the butter.</li>
  <li>Serve and enjoy.</li>
</ol>
